# License Summary (Easy Read)

This project is licensed under the **Apache License 2.0**.

### ✅ What you *can* do
- Use the code freely in personal, academic, or commercial projects.
- Modify the source code and create your own versions.
- Distribute your modified or original versions, **as long as you include the license and attribution**.

### ⚠️ What you *must* do
- Keep the license notice in your distributions.
- Include a copy of the full `LICENSE` file if you share the code.
- State any major changes you make if you redistribute a modified version.

### 🚫 What you *cannot* do
- You can’t remove the copyright or license notice.
- You can’t hold the original authors liable for any damages or problems caused by using the code.

### 📄 TL;DR
You can basically use it however you want — just credit the original authors and keep the license intact.

For full details, see the [Apache License 2.0](https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0).
